        <center><h1>Remedies for Anti-agening</h1></center>
        <h2>#1. Honey and Lemon Juice</h2>
        <p>Lemon is loaded with antioxidants and vitamin C, while, honey act as a natural antibacterial and anti-inflammatory moisturizer on your skin.

            Fresh lemon juice helps to bleach dark spots on the skin. The combination of honey and lemon juice together make your skin tighten and lighten.
            <img src="https://www.beinghappymom.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/word-image-38-862x1024.jpeg">
           <br> How to use</br>
            
            <br>Squeeze the juice of a half lemon</br>
            <br> Add 1 tablespoon of raw honey into the lemon juice and mix well</br>
            <br> Apply the mixture on your finely cleansed face</br>
            <br>Keep for 20 minutes</br>
            <br> Wash off with lukewarm water</br>
            <br>If you apply on a daily basis, you may get results between 2-3 months time.</br>  
        </p>

        <h3>#2. Coconut Milk as Home Remedy</h3>
        <p>Coconut milk is a rich source of vitamins C and E. The high levels of Vitamin C helps to protect the skin elasticity and flexibility. While Vitamin E softens the skin with antioxidant properties.

            Besides these, the rich content of copper in the coconut milk prevents wrinkles, sagging skin and age spots.
            <img src="https://www.beinghappymom.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/word-image-39-1024x683.jpeg">
       
            <br>How to use</br>
            
           <br> Method 1</br>
            
            <br>Take 3-4 tablespoon of coconut milk</br>
            <br> Dip a cotton ball in coconut milk and apply on the face</br>
            <br> Rinse with cool water after 20 minutes</br>
            <br> Method 2</br>
            
            <br>Soak 5-6 almonds overnight</br>
            <br> Peel their skins off and grind to form a smooth paste by adding 5-6 drops of coconut milk in the morning</br>
            <br>Apply the mixture on the face and leave for 15 minutes</br>
            <br>Later wash off with cold water</p>
            
